[B] Belgium - from expatica.com 31 Mar 2003
<http://www.expatica.com/belgium.asp?pad=88,89,&item_id=30102>
A soldier is believed to be the first Belgian [case] of SARS. The
suspected victim is recently-returned soldier who was based in the
Vietnamese capital, Hanoi. The unidentified male is currently receiving
treatment at a Liege hospital.
